個SER都有連登仔係到,但係大家自己集中係ルルイエ、舞鶴<br />\n<br />\nQ:入唔到我地個SER點算?<br />\nA:建議照玩,因為隻GAME唔算多互動性,就算同一個SER都係自己玩自己<br />\n<br />\nQ:幾時突破好?<br />\nA:建議盡量升爆左隻艦先.因為突破左之後會十分食油<br />\n<br />\nQ:唔夠打下一個圖阿 點算?<br />\nA:你要有足夠既肝力,肝爆上一個圖 直到可以打下一個圖[/quote]<br />\n<br />\nQ:限pool嘅艦會唔會出係普通pool?<br />\nA:會,不過唔知幾時會有,等唔到就課啦"},{"pid":"a81f0d3bd956a3f43cbfe28ecabb8dd738964a13","tid":480562,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:44:30.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f35315288532a75b4906eb585f7304f9b328f80f","tid":480562,"uid":32433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:49:01.000Z","msg":"留...名!"},{"pid":"494899afb9795af78cba5f54d4359c72336478a0","tid":480562,"uid":102542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T10:01:05.000Z","msg":"一航無論演習/推圖都屈晒機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先手升到高LV,對面都未起飛已打爆晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf88bb5615662f40e46e559798ff1b32266d06e5","tid":480562,"uid":86937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:16:20.000Z","msg":"個post已經兩日前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b2f86c5aed4d364d3f98ff50572a9d97e553d6","tid":480562,"uid":32433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個post已經兩日前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去錯post 呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/480560/page/25\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/480560/page/25</a><br />\n<br />\n係咪同我一樣block咗條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}